Form Element - Multi-line Text Input - cml:textarea

- Renders a multi-line text area
- Accepts all Common Attributes

[code] <cml:textarea label="Sample text area:" /> [/code]

<img src="sample_text_field.png" />

Additional attributes

[code] default [/code]
If supplied, the value of this attribute will be pre-filled in the text area when the page is loaded. It will not be submitted and will fail the [code]required[/code] validator until the contributor enters text into it.